text.tspan: - MK8S-001 |Wall Clipping - it has a serious effect on the game, especially as
you play through the Cherry Cup, Crossover Cup, Delfino Square/Plaza and Coconut Mall.
- MK8S-002 | Mud and tracks being moved by a few pixels and not returning to normal (Ruins Gameplay)
and not being able to remove checkpoints from levels which can break entire systems and tracks.
- MK8S-003 | It sometimes says you're in 1st or 2nd even though you're not and you sometimes end up
losing the race because of that.
- MK8S-004 | 3DS Neo Bowser City currently does not allow you to pass under or drive on top of the bridge
that overlaps the beginning of the track.
